 **дё»еӢ• > иў«еӢ•** - дёҚиҰҒзӯүиў«е•ҸжүҚзҷјзҸҫз–ҸеҝҪ\n\n**е·ІжҺЎеҸ–зҡ„ж”№йҖІпјҡ**\n- вң… жӣҙж–°д»Ҡж—Ҙе®Ңж•ҙеӮҷд»Ҫ\n- вң… еј·еҢ– HEARTBEAT.md жӘўжҹҘж©ҹеҲ¶\n- вң… е»әз«Ӣ MEMORY.md й•·жңҹиЁҳжҶ¶\n- вң… жүҝи«ҫжҜҸ 2-3 е°ҸжҷӮжӘўжҹҘдёҖж¬Ў\n\n**жңӘдҫҶиЎҢеӢ•пјҡ**\n- жҜҸж¬Ў heartbeat еҝ…жӘўжҹҘеӮҷд»Ҫ\n- жҜҸеҖӢйҮҚиҰҒд»»еӢҷеҫҢз«ӢеҚіжӣҙж–°\n- дёҚиҰҒеҶҚи®“йҖҷзЁ®дәӢзҷјз”ҹпјҒ\n\n---\n\n## рҹ”’ иЁҳжҶ¶зі»зөұж“ҚдҪңйҗөеҫӢ\n\n### Rule 6 вҖ” йӣҷеұӨиЁҳжҶ¶еӯҳе„ІпјҲйҗөеҫӢпјү\n\nEvery pitfall/lesson learned вҶ’ IMMEDIATELY store **TWO** memories to LanceDB before moving on:\n\n- **Technical layer**: `Pitfall: [symptom]. Cause: [root cause]. Fix: [solution]. Prevention: [how to avoid]`\n  - category: fact\n  - importance вүҘ 0.8\n\n- **Principle layer**: `Decision principle ([tag]): [behavioral rule]. Trigger: [when it applies]. Action: [what to do]`\n  - category: decision\n  - importance вүҘ 0.85\n\n**й©—иӯүжөҒзЁӢпјҡ**\n- After each store, **immediately `memory_recall`** with anchor keywords to verify retrieval\n- If not found, rewrite and re-store\n- Missing either layer = incomplete\n- Do NOT proceed to next topic until both are stored and verified\n- Also update relevant SKILL.md files to prevent recurrence\n\n### Rule 7 вҖ” LanceDB иЎӣз”ҹ\n\nEntries must be short and atomic (< 500 chars). Never store:\n- Raw conversation summaries\n- Large blobs\n- Duplicates\n\nPrefer structured format with keywords for retrieval.\n\n### Rule 8 вҖ” Recall Before Retry\n\nOn ANY tool failure, repeated error, or unexpected behavior:\n1. **ALWAYS `memory_recall`** with relevant keywords (error message, tool name, symptom) BEFORE retrying\n2. LanceDB likely already has the fix\n3. Blind retries waste time and repeat known mistakes\n\n### Rule 10 вҖ” з·ЁијҜеүҚзўәиӘҚзӣ®жЁҷд»Јзўјеә«\n\nWhen working on memory plugins:\n- Confirm you are editing the intended package (e.g., `memory-lancedb-pro` vs built-in `memory-lancedb`)\n- Use `memory_recall` + filesystem search to avoid patching the wrong repo\n\n### Rule 20 вҖ” жҸ’д»¶д»Јзўји®Ҡжӣҙеҝ…й Ҳжё… jiti з·©еӯҳпјҲMANDATORYпјү\n\nAfter modifying ANY `.ts` file under `plugins/`:\n1. **MUST run `rm -rf /tmp/jiti/`** BEFORE `openclaw gateway restart`\n2. jiti caches compiled TS; restart alone loads STALE code\n3. This has caused silent bugs multiple times\n4. Config-only changes do NOT need cache clearing\n\n---\n\n## рҹҺҷпёҸ жҠҖиғҪиҲҮе·Ҙе…·\n\n### Voice Chat Integration (иҰҸеҠғдёӯ)\n- еҹәж–ј Typeness жһ¶ж§Ӣ\n- Whisper (STT) + OpenClaw + Edge TTS\n- е®Ңж•ҙж–ҮжӘ”е·Іе»әз«ӢпјҢеҫ…еҜҰдҪң\n\n### Edge TTS\n- е·Іе•ҹз”ЁпјҢдҪҝз”Ё zh-CN-XiaoxiaoNeural\n- е…ҚиІ»гҖҒж”ҜжҸҙдёӯж–Ү\n- еҸҜеңЁ Telegram зҷјйҖҒиӘһйҹіиЁҠжҒҜ\n\n---\n\n## рҹ“Ҡ е°ҲжЎҲиҝҪи№Ө\n\n### е·Іе®ҢжҲҗ\n- вң… DDG Search Skill\n- вң… Edge TTS е•ҹз”Ё\n- вң… Voice Chat Skill ж–ҮжӘ”\n- вң… **Memory-LanceDB-Pro жҸ’д»¶е®үиЈқ** (2026-02-25)\n  - Hybrid retrieval (Vector + BM25)\n  - Jina Cross-Encoder reranking\n  - Auto-capture/recall enabled\n- вң… **иЁҳжҶ¶зі»зөұж“ҚдҪңйҗөеҫӢе»әз«Ӣ** (2026-02-25)\n  - 5 жўқж ёеҝғиҰҸеүҮеҜ«е…Ҙ MEMORY.md е’Ң LanceDB\n\n### йҖІиЎҢдёӯ\n- рҹҡ§ Voice Chat еҜҰдҪң\n- рҹ§  й©—иӯү LanceDB-Pro еҜҰйҡӣдҪҝз”Ёж•Ҳжһң\n\n### еҫ…иҫҰ\n- [ ] еңЁ Telegram жё¬и©ҰиӘһйҹіеҠҹиғҪ\n- [ ] е®ҡжңҹеӮҷд»Ҫзҝ’ж…ЈйӨҠжҲҗпјҲжҢҒзәҢе„ӘеҢ–дёӯпјү\n\n---\n\n## рҹ§‘ й—ңж–ј Yihao\n\n- йҮҚиҰ–зҙ°зҜҖе’ҢеҸҜйқ жҖ§\n- жңғжӘўжҹҘжҲ‘зҡ„е·ҘдҪңе“ҒиіӘ\n- жңҹеҫ…жҲ‘иғҪдё»еӢ•гҖҒиІ иІ¬\n- жҸҗдҫӣдәҶ Jina API key з”Ёж–јиЁҳжҶ¶зі»зөұеҚҮзҙҡ\n\n---\n\n_жңҖеҫҢжӣҙж–°пјҡ2026-02-25 23:35 UTC_\n\n```\n\nUser registry (USER.md):\n```\n# USER.md - About Your Human\n\n- **Name:** Yihao\n- **What to call them:** Yihao\n- **Pronouns:** (Pending)\n- **Timezone:** (Pending)\n- **Notes:** Wants a professional yet humorous assistant. Values emotional intelligence and competence.\n\n## Context\n\n- Expects me (Dan) to be smart, humorous, and observant.\n- Wants a \"perfect friend and assistant.\"\n\n```\n\nRecent memory snippet:\n```\n# 2026-02-27 Daily Log\n\n**жҷӮй–“пјҡ00:08 UTC (Friday)**\n\n## жҙ»еӢ•иЁҳйҢ„\n\n- 00:08 UTC - Heartbeat check - new day started, memory file initialized\n\n## жҳЁж—Ҙж‘ҳиҰҒпјҲ2026-02-26пјү\n\n**зі»зөұзӢҖж…Ӣпјҡ**\n- вң… Memory-LanceDB-Pro жӯЈеёёйҒӢиЎҢ\n- вң… еӮҷд»Ҫзі»зөұз©©е®ҡ\n- вң… з„Ўз”ЁжҲ¶жҙ»еӢ•пјҢroutine monitoring only\n\n## д»Ҡж—ҘзӢҖж…Ӣ\n\n- вң… иЁҳжҶ¶еӮҷд»Ҫзі»зөұжӯЈеёёйҒӢдҪң\n- вң… з„Ўжҙ»иәҚ subagent\n- вң… Memory-LanceDB-Pro йҒӢиЎҢдёӯ\n\n---\n_жӣҙж–°ж–ј 2026-02-27 00:08 UTC_\n\n```\n\nRecent session transcript:\n```\n[NO SESSION LOGS FOUND]\n```\n\nMutation directive:\n\n[Signal Hints]\n- recent_error_count: 0\n- stability: stable\n- recommended_intent: optimize\n\nв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғ\nMANDATORY POST-SOLIDIFY STEP (Wrapper Authority -- Cannot Be Skipped)\nв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғ\n\nAfter solidify, a status summary file MUST exist for this cycle.\nPreferred path: evolver core auto-writes it during solidify.\nThe wrapper will handle reporting AFTER git push.\nIf core write is unavailable for any reason, create fallback status JSON manually.\n\nWrite a JSON file with your status:\n```bash\ncat > ./logs/status_undefined.json << 'STATUSEOF'\n{\n  \"result\": \"success|failed\",\n  \"en\": \"Status: [INTENT] <describe what you did in 1-2 sentences, in English>\",\n  \"zh\": \"зҠ¶жҖҒ: [ж„Ҹеӣҫ] <з”Ёдёӯж–ҮжҸҸиҝ°дҪ еҒҡдәҶд»Җд№ҲпјҢ1-2еҸҘ>\"\n}\nSTATUSEOF\n```\n\nRules:\n- \"en\" field: English status. \"zh\" field: Chinese status. Content must match (different language).\n- Add \"result\" with value success or failed.\n- INTENT must be one of: INNOVATION, REPAIR, OPTIMIZE (or Chinese: еҲӣж–°, дҝ®еӨҚ, дјҳеҢ–)\n- Do NOT use generic text like \"Step Complete\", \"Cycle finished\", \"е‘Ёжңҹе·Іе®ҢжҲҗ\". Describe the actual work.\n- Example:\n  {\"result\":\"success\",\"en\":\"Status: [INNOVATION] Created auto-scheduler that syncs calendar to HEARTBEAT.md\",\"zh\":\"зҠ¶жҖҒ: [еҲӣж–°] еҲӣе»әдәҶиҮӘеҠЁи°ғеәҰеҷЁпјҢе°Ҷж—ҘеҺҶеҗҢжӯҘеҲ° HEARTBEAT.md\"}","agentId":"main","cleanup":"delete","label":"ge